Evidence: [frontend/src/router/index.js:42](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/router/index.js#L42), [src/edu_cloud/api/deps.py:60](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/deps.py#L60), [src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py:31](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py#L31), [src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py:45](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py#L45), [src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py:61](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py#L61), [src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py:81](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/school/settings_router.py#L81)  
Impact: `principal`/`academic_director` 被定义为 school-scoped 角色，但后端只校验 `MANAGE_SCHOOL_SETTINGS`，完全信任路径里的 `school_id`。任一本校管理员只要改 URL，就能读取或修改其他学校的 settings/modules，属于跨校越权。  
Suggested action: 在 settings router 增加 scope guard。对 school-scoped 角色强制 `school_id == current["current_role"].school_id`；平台/区域角色按明确策略放行。补一个负向回归测试，验证 principal 访问其他学校返回 403。

